Description: Tailored for topic modeling with tweets and fit for
        visualization tasks in R. Collect, pre-process and analyze the
        contents of tweets using LDA and structural topic models (STM).
        Comes with visualizing capabilities like tweet and hashtag maps
        and built-in support for 'LDAvis'.
